{"tid":2018762,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"手足被判四年後，第一個清晨","createTime":"2020-05-15T21:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T07:04:18.000Z","uid":353635,"like":146,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a03f0770f6ff4f433fa430b24fbcd6abbe673efb","tid":2018762,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:27:57.000Z","msg":"手足被判四年後，第一個清晨。<br />\n唔知佢係未同我一樣無眠，<br />\n聽緊一樣的雀仔聲，<br />\n睇緊一樣的微光。<br />\n唔知佢媽媽、佢女朋友，<br />\n係未都訓唔到，<br />\n聽緊一樣的雀仔聲。<br />\n<br />\n其實，係入面個個都好有可能係我，<br />\n跑慢幾秒、遲疑幾秒，<br />\n身陷囹圄的就係我。<br />\n<br />\n我想像唔到，<br />\n假如612我已被捕，<br />\n睇住示威愈演愈大，<br />\n睇住咁多人聲援自己，<br />\n但同時又愈來愈多警暴以及各種荒謬之事，<br />\n我會如何自處；<br />\n面對法律程序的壓力，<br />\n以及被剝奪四年的時光，<br />\n內心又有多麼窒息。<br />\n<br />\n唔係好知，自己咁微薄的力量，<br />\n可以為場運動貢獻到咩，<br />\n淨係可以間唔時提下自己，<br />\n唔好做港豬，<br />\n不過點都係要行落去，<br />\n因為我條氣唔順。"},{"pid":"f7bb76b4c57fa1251342adf1f05baa9eca5d2e85","tid":2018762,"uid":41490,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:29:40.000Z","msg":"我地要代佢地行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5673ad76bb89e2718afe249cd5500a6e82d0c6","tid":2018762,"uid":263436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be8a29ff591d5707977d8cb6636902f0772d146","tid":2018762,"uid":218,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:32:49.000Z","msg":"首先要戴好頭盔<br />\n唔好撈亂夢境同現實<br />\n打壓只會越嚟越勁<br />\n講得越多嘢即係交越多料比班狗同狗官"},{"pid":"634da56191bcb66eddf55651e084f635d0435249","tid":2018762,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb23ed8b0001bd4c2b8fc31b359dd13a6769ddfb","tid":2018762,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05